Suddha
Parittattika
Paṭiccavāra
Paccayapaccanīya
Saṅkhyāvāra
Suddha
25.
1951Nahetuyā ekaṃ, naārammaṇe pañca, naadhipatiyā dasa, naanantare pañca, nasamanantare pañca, naaññamaññe naupanissaye pañca, napurejāte dvādasa, napacchājāte terasa, naāsevane terasa, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye najhāne namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte pañca, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā pañca, novigate pañca. (Evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)
1952Paccanīyaṃ.
